ỗ trợ tham gia c&aacute;c kh&oacute;a học chuy&ecirc;n m&ocirc;n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p4\">&bull; Thưởng Lễ, Tết, sinh nhật, thai sản, ốm đau, hiếu hỉ</p>\r\n<p class=\"p4\"><strong>Thời gian l&agrave;m việc</strong>:<span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"p4\">- Thời gian l&agrave;m việc fulltime T2-T6 từ 8h30-17h30 hoặc 9h00-18h00 (c&oacute; thể sắp xếp giờ l&agrave;m việc với leader), nghỉ trưa 1 tiếng từ 12h00-13h00</p>\r\n<p class=\"p4\">C&Ocirc;NG TY CỔ PHẦN THE FIRST ONE</p>\r\n<p class=\"p5\"><span class=\"s1\">Website: </span><span class=\"s2\">https://thefirstone.jp/</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"p4\">Văn ph&ograve;ng TFO: số 108 Phố Nguyễn Ho&agrave;ng, Mỹ Đ&igrave;nh 2, Nam Từ Li&ecirc;m, H&agrave; Nội</p>\r\n<p class=\"p4\">SĐT: 0246.259.6061</p>','uploads/documents/1b44d1e61c.docx','uploads/thumbnails/1b44d1e61c.jpg','2025-04-24 19:56:51'),(7,8,'writing 1','<p dir=\"ltr\"><span>Question 1: Read the e-mail below.</span></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><span>From: Sunshine Bakery</span></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><span>To: Local Residents</span></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><span>Subject: New Bakery Opening</span></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><span>Sent: October 10, 09:00 A.M.</span></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><span>Dear Residents,</span></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><span>We are excited to announce the opening of our new bakery in your neighborhood. We offer fresh bread, cakes, and pastries made daily. If you have any special requests or ideas for flavors you would like to see in the future, please feel free to share them with us.</span></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><span>Thank you,</span></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><span>Sunshine Bakery</span></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><span>Directions: </span><span>Respond to the e-mail as if you are a local resident. In your e-mail, give TWO suggestions regarding the products and ask one question.</span></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><span>Đ&aacute;p &aacute;n:</span></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><span>Dear Sunshine Bakery,</span></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><span>I received your email regarding the opening of your new bakery.</span></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><span>I am very excited to have a bakery nearby, and I have a couple of suggestions. Firstly, it would be wonderful if you could offer gluten-free options for those with dietary restrictions. Secondly, I think adding seasonal flavors, such as pumpkin during fall or strawberry in spring, would make your bakery even more special.</span></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><span>By the way, what are your operating hours? I look forward to visiting soon.</span></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><span>Thank you,</span><span><br /></span><span>&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><span>Question 2: Read the e-mail below.</span></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><span>From: Adventure Travel</span></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><span>To: Travel Enthusiasts</span><span><br /></span><span>Subject: Winter Skiing Tour Promotion</span></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><span>Sent: November 15, 10:30 A.M.</span></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><span>Adventure Travel is offering a special winter skiing tour to the Alps. Our package includes ski lessons, equipment rentals, and transportation. For more details, please contact us via email at info@adventuretravel.com</span></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><span>Directions: </span><span>Respond to the e-mail as if you are interested in the tour. In your e-mail, ask for three pieces of information about the skiing tour package.</span></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><span>Đ&aacute;p &aacute;n:</span></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><span>Dear Adventure Travel,</span></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><span>Thank you for your email regarding the winter skiing tour. I am very interested in booking the tour for my family.</span></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><span>I would appreciate it if you could provide more information on the following:</span></p>\r\n<ol>\r\n<li dir=\"ltr\">\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><span>What is included in the ski lessons (e.g., duration, skill levels)?</span></p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li dir=\"ltr\">\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><span>What type of equipment is provided in the rental package</span></p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li dir=\"ltr\">\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><span>How long does the trip last, and when does it start?</span></p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><span>Thank you, and I look forward to hearing from you.</span></p>\r\n<h3 dir=\"ltr\"><span>Question 3: Write an opinion essay</span></h3>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><span>Directions: </span><span>Read the question below. You will have 30 minutes to plan, write, and revise your essay. Typically, an effective essay will contain a minimum of 300 words.</span></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><span>Some people prefer living in a city, while others prefer living in the countryside. What are the advantages and disadvantages of living in a city? Give specific reasons and examples to support your opinion.</span></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><span>Đ&aacute;p &aacute;n:</span><span> Living in a city has both advantages and disadvantages. One of the main advantages is the convenience of access to services and amenities. In cities, you can find many options for shopping, entertainment, and healthcare, all within a short distance. Additionally, cities tend to have better job opportunities, especially in specialized fields like finance or technology. For example, when I worked in marketing, living in the city allowed me to attend networking events and job fairs easily, which contributed to my career growth.</span></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><span>However, there are also disadvantages to living in a city. The most obvious one is the cost of living, which tends to be higher in urban areas. Rent, food, and transportation costs can add up quickly. Moreover, cities are often more polluted, which can affect your health and overall well-being. The noise and constant activity in cities can also be overwhelming and stressful, especially for those who prefer a quieter lifestyle.</span></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><span>In conclusion, while living in a city offers many conveniences, the high cost of living and the stress of urban life are important factors to consider. Ultimately, the decision between living in a city or the countryside depends on individual preferences and lifestyle choices.</span></p>\r\n<div><span><br /></span></div>','uploads/documents/fdcd81e622.pdf','uploads/thumbnails/fdcd81e622.jpg','2025-04-24 21:26:06'),(8,8,'writing 2','<h2 dir=\"ltr\"><span>Toeic Writing Test 2</span></h2>\r\n<h3 dir=\"ltr\"><span>Questions 1-5: Write a sentence based on a picture - Test 2</span></h3>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><span>Directions: Write ONE sentence that is based on the picture using the TWO words or phrases under it. You may change the forms of the words and you may use them in any order.</span></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><span>Question 1: waiter, tray</span></p>\r\n<p><span><span><br /></span></span></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><span>Đ&aacute;p &aacute;n:</span><span> The waiter is carrying a tray with drinks to the customers at the table.</span></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><span>Question 2: laptop, office</span></p>\r\n<p><span><span><br /></span></span></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><span>Đ&aacute;p &aacute;n:</span><span> The employee is working on his laptop in the office during lunch break.</span></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><span>Question 3: tree, park</span></p>\r\n<p><span><span><br /></span></span></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><span>Đ&aacute;p &aacute;n:</span><span> The children are playing under the tree in the park on a sunny day.</span></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><span>Question 4: shoes, shelf</span></p>\r\n<p><span><span><br /></span></span></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><span>Đ&aacute;p &aacute;n:</span><span> The shoes are neatly arranged on the shelf near the door.</span></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><span>Question 5: books, shelf</span></p>\r\n<p><span><span><br /></span></span></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><span>Đ&aacute;p &aacute;n:</span><span> The books are placed in order on the shelf in the library.</span></p>\r\n<h3 dir=\"ltr\"><span>Questions 6-7: Respond to a written request - Test 2</span></h3>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><span>Question 6: Read the e-mail below.</span></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><span>From: Green Valley Hotel</span></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><span>To: Guests</span></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><span>Subject: Upcoming Renovation</span></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><span>Sent: February 20, 11:00 A.M.</span></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><span>Dear Guests,</span></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><span>We would like to inform you that our hotel will be undergoing renovations starting next month. We are working to enhance our facilities and provide you with a more comfortable experience. During the renovation period, some areas may be temporarily unavailable. We apologize for any inconvenience this may cause. Please let us know if you have any questions or concerns.</span></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><span>Best regards,</span></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><span>Green Valley Hotel</span></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><span>Directions:</span><span> Respond to the e-mail as if you are a guest. In your e-mail, express your thoughts about the renovation and ask one question.</span></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><span>Đ&aacute;p &aacute;n:</span></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><span>Dear Green Valley Hotel,</span></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><span>Thank you for informing us about the upcoming renovations.</span></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><span>I understand that this will be a temporary inconvenience, but I am happy to hear that the hotel will be improving its facilities. I have enjoyed staying at your hotel in the past, and I&rsquo;m sure the renovations will make my future stays even better.</span></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><span>By the way, will the renovations affect the availability of the swimming pool and fitness center? I&rsquo;d appreciate it if you could let me know.</span></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><span>Best regards,</span></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><span>&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><span>Question 7: Read the e-mail below.</span></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><span>From: Global Tech</span></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><span>To: Employees</span></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><span>Subject: New Employee Training Program</span></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><span>Sent: March 5, 10:00 A.M.</span></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><span>Dear Team,</span></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><span>We are excited to announce the launch of a new training program designed to improve our employees\' skills in digital marketing. The program will include online modules and live workshops. Please respond to this email to register for the program. We believe this program will be beneficial to your career development.</span></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><span>Best regards,</span></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><span>Global Tech</span></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><span>Directions: Respond to the e-mail as if you are an employee. In your e-mail, express your interest in the program and ask two questions.</span></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><span>Đ&aacute;p &aacute;n:</span></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><span>Dear Global Tech,</span></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><span>Thank you for the announcement regarding the new employee training program. I am very interested in improving my digital marketing skills, and I would like to register for the program.</span></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><span>I have two questions:</span></p>\r\n<ol>\r\n<li dir=\"ltr\">\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><span>Will the online modules be available for us to complete at our own pace, or do they require a specific schedule?</span></p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li dir=\"ltr\">\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><span>Will the live workshops be held virtually, or will they take place at the office?</span></p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><span>Thank you, and I look forward to the training.</span></p>\r\n<p><span><span><br /></span></span></p>\r\n<h3 dir=\"ltr\"><span>Question 8: Write an opinion essay - Test 2</span></h3>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><span>Directions: Read the question below. You will have 30 minutes to plan, write, and revise your essay. Typically, an effective essay will contain a minimum of 300 words.</span></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><span>Do you agree or disagree with the statement that technology has made our lives easier? Use specific reasons and examples to support your opinion.</span></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><span>Đ&aacute;p &aacute;n:</span></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><span>I agree that technology has made our lives easier in many ways. One of the key areas where technology has improved our lives is communication. With the development of smartphones and social media, we can now connect with people from all over the world instantly. For example, I am able to stay in touch with family and friends who live far away, thanks to video calls and messaging apps.</span></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><span>In addition to communication, technology has also transformed the way we work and shop. Many people now work from home, using online tools and platforms to collaborate with colleagues. For instance, I can attend virtual meetings and access documents from anywhere, which makes my work more flexible. Similarly, online shopping has become a convenient way to purchase products, saving time and effort.</span></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><span>Furthermore, technology has revolutionized healthcare. Medical advancements, such as telemedicine and wearable health devices, have made it easier for people to monitor their health and access medical advice from home. My smartwatch, for example, tracks my heart rate and physical activity, helping me stay healthy.</span></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><span>However, while technology has brought many benefits, it is important to recognize its drawbacks, such as increased screen time and privacy concerns. Despite these challenges, I believe that technology has overall made our lives easier by improving communication, work efficiency, and healthcare.</span></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><span>In conclusion, I strongly agree that technology has made life easier, as it provides us with numerous tools to improve our personal and professional lives.</span></p>\r\n<div><span><br /></span></div>','uploads/documents/31c5f836b9.pdf','uploads/thumbnails/31c5f836b9.jpg','2025-04-24 21:30:31');
